<eesti>&sect; 46. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 46. </inglise>
<eesti>Seaduse j&otilde;ustumine </eesti>
<inglise>Entry into force of Act </inglise>
<eesti>K&auml;esolev seadus j&otilde;ustub 1999. aasta 1. juulil. </eesti>
<inglise>This Act enters into force on 1 July 1999. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 47. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 47. </inglise>
<eesti>Audiitorkogu moodustamine </eesti>
<inglise>Formation of Board of Auditors </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Audiitorkogu moodustavad ja audiitorite nimekirja kantakse k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisel audiitorid, kellel on kehtiv Audiitortegevuse N&otilde;ukogu poolt v&auml;ljastatud audiitori kutsetunnistus. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Upon the entry into force of this Act, auditors who hold a valid professional licence of an auditor issued by the Auditing Board shall form the Board of Auditors and shall be entered in the list of auditors. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Audiitorkogu esimese &uuml;ldkoosoleku kutsub kokku rahandusminister kolme kuu jooksul k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Minister of Finance shall call the first general meeting of the Board of Auditors within three months after the entry into force of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>Esimene &uuml;ldkoosolek valib audiitorkogu juhatuse ja revisjonikomisjoni liikmed, kes astuvad ametisse valimise hetkest, ning esindajad kutsekomisjoni. </eesti>
<inglise>The first general meeting shall elect the management board of the Board of Auditors and the members of the audit committee who assume office as of the moment of the election, and the representatives in the professional qualifications committee. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 48. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 48. </inglise>
<eesti>Kutsekomisjoni moodustamine </eesti>
<inglise>Formation of professional qualifications committee </inglise>
<eesti>Kutsekomisjoni moodustab Vabariigi Valitsus &uuml;he kuu jooksul p&auml;rast audiitorkogu loomist. </eesti>
<inglise>The professional qualifications committee shall be formed by the Government of the Republic within one month after the formation of the Board of Auditors. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 49. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 49. </inglise>
<eesti>Seaduse kohaldamine audiitoritele, kellele on audiitori kutsetunnistus v&auml;ljastatud enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist </eesti>
<inglise>Application of Act to auditors to whom professional licence of auditor has been issued prior to entry into force of this Act </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Audiitorid, kellele on audiitori kutsetunnistus v&auml;ljastatud enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist, esitavad k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 27 s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uetele vastava tegevusaruande audiitorkogu juhatuse m&auml;&auml;ratud t&auml;htajal, kuid mitte hiljem kui kaks aastat p&auml;rast k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Auditors to whom a professional licence of auditor has been issued prior to the entry into force of this Act shall submit activity reports in compliance with the requirements provided for in &sect; 27 of this Act during the term specified by the management board of the Board of Auditors but not later than two years after the entry into force of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Audiitoritele, kellele on audiitori kutsetunnistus v&auml;ljastatud enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist, ei laiene k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 21 l&otilde;ike 1 punktis 4 s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uded. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Requirements provided for in clause 21 (1) 4) of this Act shall not extend to auditors to whom a professional licence of auditor has been issued prior to the entry into force of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 50. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 50. </inglise>
