<inglise>Amendment of State Fees Act </inglise>
<eesti>Riigil&otilde;ivuseadust (RT I 1997, 80, 1344; RT I 2001, 55, 331; 56, 332; 64, 367; 65, 377; 85, 512; 88, 531; 91, 543; 93, 565; 2002, 1, 1; 18, 97) t&auml;iendatakse &sect;-ga 197 (2) j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>Section 1972 is added to the State Fees Act (RT I 1997, 80, 1344; RT I 2001, 55, 331; 56, 332; 64, 367; 65, 377; 85, 512; 88, 531; 91, 543; 93, 565; 2002, 1, 1; 18, 97) worded as follows: </inglise>
